WEBVTT

1
00:03:36.760 --> 00:03:38.750 
杰克!
Jake!

2
00:03:38.760 --> 00:03:40.720 
老妈把我禁足两周
Mom grounded me for two weeks.

3
00:03:40.730 --> 00:03:42.080 
你妈为啥没把这事告诉我?
Why didn't your mother tell me about this?

4
00:03:42.090 --> 00:03:44.270 
我跟她保证我会告诉你
I promised I'd tell you.

5
00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:47.350 
我能说啥啊? 她信任我
What can I say? She believed me.

6
00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:49.920 
去看场电影咋样? 父子小聚一下
So how about a movie? A little father-son bonding.

7
00:03:49.930 --> 00:03:51.540 
不 不能看电影
No,no. No movies.

8
00:03:51.550 --> 00:03:53.150 
-那溜冰? -也不能溜冰
-Skating? -No skating.

9
00:03:53.160 --> 00:03:53.750 
好吧
Fine.

10
00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:56.260 
还不能看电视 不能打电玩
Also no TV,no video games,

11
00:03:56.270 --> 00:03:57.730 
不能用手机 不能听IPod
no cell phones,and no iPods--

12
00:03:57.740 --> 00:03:59.950 
不能碰任何消遣或娱乐工具
nothing that gives you any amusement or enjoyment.

13
00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:01.920 
你干嘛不拿皮带抽我一顿 然后让这事过去得了?
Couldn't you just smack me with a belt and get it over with?

14
00:04:01.930 --> 00:04:04.850 
滚一边去
Get out of here.

15
00:04:07.440 --> 00:04:10.310 
我无聊死了啊
I'm bored.

